{
  "stem": "5639.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We all spoke German, because we also studied German at school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And working in his shop put me in touch with a, a class of Jewish people that I never knew before.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if I knew them, I always knew them from the position of being the benefactor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I found myself in a very disadvantaged position.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't speak Yiddish, although my parents, among themselves, spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They spoke Polish, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "To us, they spoke only Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I, I was surrounded by Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "One of my grandmothers never learned Polish, and never bothered to learn Polish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Maybe she thought it's Polish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But she was very comfortable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She didn't need Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The shops in our house were owned by Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The newspaper that she read was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Her housekeeper was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Her children were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So she lived in a-- in a--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In an environment that she needed no other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A whole environ-- she probably never realize that the Russians left Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- and that's it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, so I heard Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I can't say that Yiddish was an alien language.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I couldn't speak it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I knew certain expressions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I couldn't conduct a conversation in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And these people with whom I work, the real tailors, the real shoemaker, the real Jewish proletariat--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Spoke--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The core of Jewish workforce--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they called me the intelligentsia, and by word, they didn't mean it as a compliment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Far from it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They made me suffer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I might be better educated than them, but I can't sew a button.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I might come from a better home than them, but I can't pedal on the machine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And these were the vital things that were needed for survival.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Work.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
